se on topics of regionality, including associated projects.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-ND 3.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/3.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 7aHISTORY / World.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z97831107195500 cEPUBz97831105849120 cprintz978311058454740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110587173zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110587173zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110587173/original  a978-3-11-071955-0 DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076248-8 DG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA